data.title: Watch Carnival of Souls Online
data.meta_description: Watch Carnival of Souls online now with AMC. Stream free with your TV provider. Browse more movies available on demand.
data.text:
Transformers

All that stands between the Decepticons and ultimate power is a clue held by young Sam Witwicky. Sam and Bumblebee, his Autobot, race against an enemy unlike anything anyone has seen before.

Legends of the Fall

A sweeping, romantic epic of three brothers, their father, and the beautiful, compelling young woman who irrevocably changes each of their lives.

The Natural

Robert Redford stars as a middle-aged baseball player with a mysterious past whose supernatural talent carries a losing team to glory.

Pretty in Pink

A girl from the wrong side of town must choose between the affections of dating her childhood sweetheart or a rich but sensitive playboy.

All of Them Witches

The untold story of the Witch and her persecution and perseverance throughout history.

Bloodsport

Jean-Claude Van Damme stars as Frank Dux, a man who refuses to lose and who might just win himself a place in history as he competes in a full-contact world championship competition.

Kill Bill: Vol. 2

The Bride continues her quest of vengeance against her former boss Bill, the bouncer Budd and the one-eyed Elle.

Kill Bill: Vol. 1

A bride looks for vengeance on the team of assassins she once worked with, when she wakes up from a four-year coma childless.

Back to School

Millionaire Thornton Melon's son is a college misfit, so Thornton lends some fatherly support..by enrolling as a fellow freshman! Who cares if he never finished high school?

Mechanic: Resurrection

Arthur Bishop thought he had put his murderous past behind him when his most formidable foe kidnaps the love of his life.

White House Down

While on a tour of the White House with his daughter, a Capitol policeman must take action to save his child and the president from an armed group of paramilitary invaders.

A Few Good Men

A young Navy lawyer risks his career to uncover the truth during a military trial.

Young Guns

A Western adventure, based on a true story, about six young men hired to guard an Englishman's ranch against a mob in 1870s New Mexico.

Sorority Girl

A poor-little-rich-girl feels alienated by her mother and enacts a string of revenges on her fellow pupils at a girls' boarding school.

Submarine Seahawk

For his first command in the Pacific war an officer is ordered to take his submarine on a reconnaissance mission to locate a fleet of Japanese fighting ships the Allies have lost track of.

Rock All Night

Cloud Nine, the local teen hangout, has been taken over by a pair of escaped killers, who hold the local teens hostage. The bartender realizes it's up to him to save the kids.

Espionage in Tangiers

A secret agent is assigned to capture a criminal gang that is threatening to destroy Earth with a death ray.

Runaway Daughters

3 teenagers are unable to adjust at home and in high-school. Tempted with an easy, carefree life they soon pass from misdemeanors into serious crime - and will suffer for it.

The Ruthless Four

A group of men embark on a mission to discover a golden treasure from a mine.

Prince of Space

When an alien force tries to invade Earth to steal a powerful new rocket fuel, a mysterious hero intervenes.

The Undead

A beautiful woman is sent back in time via hypnosis to the Middle Ages where she finds she is suspected of being a witch, and subject to being executed.

Real Genius

Three brainy college students plot an elaborate revenge when they learn they've been inadvertently working on a secret weapon for the military.

Fast Times at Ridgemont High

A group of Southern California high school students are enjoying their most important subjects: sex, drugs, and rock n' roll.

The Fifth Element

In the colorful future, a cab driver unknowingly becomes the center of the search for a legendary cosmic weapon to keep Evil and Mr. Zorg at bay.

The Expendables 3

When The Expendables face an old rival, it's a clash of old-school versus high-tech in the most personal battle yet.

Enemy of the State

Robert Clayton Dean is a successful Washington, D.C. attorney who - without his knowledge - is given a video that ties a top official of the National Security Agency to a political murder!
